{"tid":589533,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加領「兵」700勝 ：重要的延續","createTime":"2018-03-12T02:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T03:27:15.000Z","uid":46892,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d7289ee356196c585c4b0d18c7e42cd7a9b0e55c","tid":589533,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:11:50.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=OiXHZpz%2BOw6Dw8c756osGgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e67af6e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿仙奴贏屈福特取得盃賽及聯賽兩連勝，亦是領隊雲加領軍以來第700場勝利，他揚言這是重要的延續。<br />\n<br />\n「我們今天取得勝利，總的來說，經過對AC米蘭後，我相信是重要的延續。屈福特在下半場反撲凌厲，但整體而言這是具說服力的勝仗，是重要的。」雲加在球隊周日以3:0大勝屈福特後說。<br />\n<br />\n這位法國名帥直言未忘之前的低潮：「我們經歷過失望的時光，球迷承受的苦楚與我們別無兩樣。然而己隊的工作是在重要時刻爭取表現及團結一致，從而在比賽中挽回球迷的支持。」<br />\n<br />\n在比賽中救出12的施治，錄得200場不失球紀錄，雲加談到這位捷克名將時謂：「這絕對是無與倫比的紀錄，那是美妙的動力、美妙的欲望及無與倫比的智慧。」"},{"pid":"3b504a525f07bd1a3a897da4e8e3d5e9cf4e89bc","tid":589533,"uid":1147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:13:04.000Z","msg":"延續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af14cab44cffc6197fd6e4c0776154117abb9a9","tid":589533,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:19:05.000Z","msg":"真正嘅旅程只係剛剛開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c1b5ab6a18455f1bc8d733a45e694daa252f32","tid":589533,"uid":2333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:20:11.000Z","msg":"永續雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c5977e9219420d0c3fab3fb9a41f1bcec171da","tid":589533,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:21:33.000Z","msg":"插住喉教 延續雲加"},{"pid":"1fcc2c8b894cb4a500786ce6734f0e6e800a3359","tid":589533,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:21:36.000Z","msg":"it is just the beginning<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb6393e740fbfcd360a583f65097e3c70869d39","tid":589533,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T03:27:15.000Z","msg":"爺爺又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，要永續啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}